      "title": "Lunch packet prices up by 10% from today",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The All Island Canteen Owners Association (AICOA) has decided to increase all foods, including vegetable rice packets by 10% from the current price.",
        "Association Chairman Asela Sampath said the decision was taken considering the increase in the fuel prices and transport costs.",
        "As such, the prices of vegetable, fish and chicken rice packets and fried rice and even Kottu will be increased by 10 percent.",
        "However, no price increase will come to effect on pain-tea, milk tea and hoppers, he added.(Cathuranga Samarawickrema)"
      ],
